  "detailed_description": "COMMAND A FLEET OF SPACESHIPS<br>Players are tasked with defending their base from swarms of enemies while embarking on an epic quest for cheese. As the commander of a formidable fleet, your primary objective is to strategically deploy a variety of spacecraft to defend against incoming threats.<br><br>Utilizing a unique blend of tower defense mechanics and RTS elements like resource management, players must skillfully collect cheese scattered throughout the cosmos to fuel their defensive efforts. Each morsel of cheese collected serves as currency, allowing you to purchase and upgrade spaceships tailored to your tactical preferences.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700650/extras/c37ac898aa4cfecb706e1d61fafb5b2b.poster.avif?t=1768488135\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700650/extras/c37ac898aa4cfecb706e1d61fafb5b2b.webm?t=1768488135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700650/extras/c37ac898aa4cfecb706e1d61fafb5b2b.mp4?t=1768488135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Attach up to 3 ships to carriers to help defend the base and gather cheese.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700650/extras/c5656fcdd11771e0b9299f5196832a3e.poster.avif?t=1768488135\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700650/extras/c5656fcdd11771e0b9299f5196832a3e.webm?t=1768488135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700650/extras/c5656fcdd11771e0b9299f5196832a3e.mp4?t=1768488135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Defend the base with abilities like missile assaults.",
